ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Canadian Wheat Board Contingency Fund Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD CONTINGENCY FUND REGULATIONS in order to increase the limit of the balance of the contingency fund to enable the Canadian Wheat Board to transfer the surplus from non-pool activities into the contingency fund.
